---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import EscherDivider from '../components/EscherDivider.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Maja Willard — mwillard.pl">
<main class="plakat">

  <section class="plakat-hero">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot">●</span> zespół filmowy mw <span class="dot">·</span> prezentuje <span class="dot">·</span> mmxxvi</div>
      <h1 class="display">Maja<br/>Will<span class="ow">ard</span></h1>
      <div class="plakat-meta">
        <b>psycholożka</b> · neuronauka poznawcza · psychodeliki · open science<br/>
        <b>malarka</b> po godzinach · czytanie tarota · obsesja na punkcie kotów<br/>
        warszawa · ORCID 0009-0005-3482-1119
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="plakat-portrait">
      <img src="/images/portrait_redglasses.jpg" alt="Maja Willard"/>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="plakat-strap">
    <span>● obsada · cast</span>
    <span>akt I → akt VI</span>
    <span>czas trwania · ∞</span>
    <span>bilety · gratis ●</span>
  </div>

  <section class="akt" id="akt-i">
    <div class="akt-num display">I</div>
    <div class="akt-label">akt pierwszy · about</div>
    <h2 class="akt-title">About <em>me(ow).</em></h2>
    <div class="akt-body">
      <p>Researcher at the Faculty of Psychology, University of Warsaw. Member of the Society for Open Science. I work on grassroots verification of neural theories of consciousness, interdisciplinary research on psychedelics, and meta-analyses of psychological meta-analyses for cultural representativeness.</p>
      <p>Earlier: language-comprehension impairments in schizophrenia, neurobiomarkers of psychosis. I'm drawn to <em>psychopharmacology, methodology and therapy efficacy research</em> — but in equal measure to grassroots organising, public-science events, and psychedelic education.</p>
      <p>In 2025 I co-created <em>CATS — Conferences Acclaiming Transparent Science</em> with Paweł L., trying to push for rigorous psychedelic science in Poland. Privately I paint, love cats, interwar Polish literature, far-too-long films, and any well-made art deco gesture.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <EscherDivider variant="x" />

  <section class="akt" id="akt-ii">
    <div class="akt-num display">II</div>
    <div class="akt-label">akt drugi · scientific chwaliposting</div>
    <h2 class="akt-title">Trzeba mieć samoocenę<br/><em>jak skały Gibraltaru.</em></h2>
    <div class="akt-pubs">
      <ul>
        <li>Wójcik, M., Orłowski, P., Adamczyk, S., et al. (submitted Jan 2026). <em>No evidence for persistent neurophysiological reorganization in long-term naturalistic psychedelic users.</em></li>
        <li>Domingos, C., Więcławski, W., Frycz, S., <strong>Wójcik, M.</strong>, Jáni, M., Dudzińska, O., Ros, T. (2025). <em>Functional connectivity in chronic schizophrenia.</em> Brain &amp; Behavior.</li>
        <li>Adamczyk, P., Więcławski, W., <strong>Wójcik, M.</strong>, Frycz, S., Panek, B., et al. (2025). <em>Aberrant information flow within the resting-state triple-network model in schizophrenia.</em> Psychiatry Research: Neuroimaging.</li>
        <li>Wójcik, M., Lenartowicz, P., Kapka, Z., Pierz, J., Skupień, J. (2025). <em>Methodological challenges in psychedelic-assisted therapy research for SUDs.</em> Preregistered review.</li>
        <li>Górski, M.R., Kubik, K., Jeleń, A., Kalinowski, M., Stefanowicz, M., Nowak, G., <strong>Wójcik, M.</strong>, et al. (under review). <em>WEIRD in, WEIRD out: cultural bias in psychological meta-analyses.</em> Psychological Bulletin.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="akt" id="akt-iii">
    <div class="akt-num display">III</div>
    <div class="akt-label">akt trzeci · communities</div>
    <h2 class="akt-title">Conferences Acclaiming<br/><em>Transparent Science.</em></h2>
    <div class="akt-body">
      <p><strong>CATS</strong> is the conference I'm a mother of — and I designed the entire site. We push for transparent, replicable, methodologically sober psychedelic science in Poland.</p>
      <p><a href="https://cats-conference.pl">cats-conference.pl</a> · with the <a href="https://s-on.pl">Society for Open Science</a> (s-on.pl, co-founder).</p>
      <p>Plus: psychedelic workshops, biology teaching, popular-science talks, doctoral seminars, a long line of student conferences at <a href="https://knsp-uj.pl">knsp-uj.pl</a> (vice-chair, archived).</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <EscherDivider variant="circles" />

  <section class="akt" id="akt-iv">
    <div class="akt-num display">IV</div>
    <div class="akt-label">akt czwarty · obowiązkowo · cats</div>
    <h2 class="akt-title">Koty.</h2>
    <div class="akt-body">
      <p>The mandatory cats section. Updated weekly with whoever has been <em>particularly virtuous</em> or <em>particularly chaotic</em>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-week-row">
      <div class="cat-week">
        <div class="lbl">nice cat of the week</div>
        <div class="nm display">Bonifacy</div>
        <div class="desc">Has finally opened up and showed the staff how much he loves belly rubs. Great progress on the trust-issues front.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cat-week">
        <div class="lbl">naughty cat of the week</div>
        <div class="nm display">Hieronim</div>
        <div class="desc">Stole treats from Daniel, his BLIND roommate. Then stole them again. Disciplinary committee in session.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-strip">
      <div class="ck"><img src="/images/cat_eged_01.jpg" alt=""/></div>
      <div class="ck"><img src="/images/cat_eged_02.jpg" alt=""/></div>
      <div class="ck"><img src="/images/cat_eged_03.jpg" alt=""/></div>
      <div class="ck"><img src="/images/cat_eged_04.jpg" alt=""/></div>
      <div class="ck"><img src="/images/cat_eged_05.jpg" alt=""/></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="akt" id="akt-v">
    <div class="akt-num display">V</div>
    <div class="akt-label">akt piąty · atelier</div>
    <h2 class="akt-title">Czemu to takie nic<br/>jest właśnie <em>czymś</em> dla mnie?</h2>
    <div class="akt-body">
      <p>An aspiring expressionist portrait painter, in admiration of Witkacy and Leon Chwistek. Side projects: collages, tarot-deck illustration, the occasional dragon. <em>Psychological-portrait-on-commission</em> coming soon-ish.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-2">
      <figure><img src="/images/painting_purplecat_street.jpg" alt=""/><figcaption>nocny zaułek z kotem · ol. 2022</figcaption></figure>
      <figure><img src="/images/painting_blackcat_alley.jpg" alt=""/><figcaption>brama · ol. 2023</figcaption></figure>
      <figure><img src="/images/painting_klimt_woman.jpg" alt=""/><figcaption>portret w stylu Klimta</figcaption></figure>
      <figure><img src="/images/painting_dragons.jpg" alt=""/><figcaption>red dragons on white mushrooms</figcaption></figure>
      <figure><img src="/images/painting_nude_blue.jpg" alt=""/><figcaption>nude · blue · studio</figcaption></figure>
      <figure><img src="/images/drawing_charcoal_venus.jpg" alt=""/><figcaption>charcoal · Venus &amp; tulips</figcaption></figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="akt" id="akt-vi" style="border-bottom:none">
    <div class="akt-num display">VI</div>
    <div class="akt-label">epilog · kontakt</div>
    <h2 class="akt-title">Kontakt — <em>i pozostałe ślady.</em></h2>
    <div class="akt-body">
      <p><a href="mailto:mayaowillard@gmail.com">mayaowillard@gmail.com</a> · +48 666 276 392<br/>
      <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Maja-Wojcik-2">researchgate</a> (old surname: Wójcik) · ORCID <span class="mono">0009-0005-3482-1119</span></p>
      <p>Or: visit the <a href="/salon/">Salon</a> for a séance. Visit the <a href="/notatnik/">Notatnik</a> for the CV side of things.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</BaseLayout>
